Yesterdays is only useful for statistics e.g SQL

init:
    setSchedule:
        getDataTomorrow @ 1430
    write yesterday
    write today

initCheck:
    now = dateTime
    
    cache = [cacheCheck()]
    if cache == None OR cache.today < today
        init()
    
    if now > toothHurty
        write tomorrow


schedule:
   if > 230
        write tomorrow
    
    write today
    write yesterday

